and you probably noticed

00:15:39.960 --> 00:15:42.960
the bulk of the bars here
are on the left side,

00:15:42.960 --> 00:15:45.710
so at the younger ages, so
you see the tallest bars

00:15:45.710 --> 00:15:49.060
are at the youngest age groups there.

